name: Delicious Midsommar Torte
desc: A small cake made from Midsommar Berries. One spoonful is all it takes to whisk you away to a lush berry forest. Amid the vibrant, lively sweetness, there is a hint of refreshing tartness imparted by the Smetana. This cake raises the festive mood to the peak!

value.text: Revives a character and restores 1,500 HP.
